research_municipality_step.notes: Teague, TX operates under a General Law Type A government, which is a mayor-council system with aldermen. James Monks was elected Mayor in May 2024. The Board of Aldermen includes Ron Rasbeary (Place I), Jerry Ballew (Place II), Rhonda Jones (Place III), Bridget Gauntt (Place IV), and Timothy Campbell (Place V). Bridget Gauntt and Timothy Campbell are both listed as Mayor Pro Tempore.
